{"tid":1418770,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"暫停勇武，直到港共記者會冇野好講。","createTime":"2019-08-05T20:20:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-05T20:29:34.000Z","uid":272573,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e953bc1268aa041229b1059f25c9e026ec07c0dc","tid":1418770,"uid":272573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:20:12.000Z","msg":"如題。<br />\n<br />\n港共昨日預告黎緊每日都有記者會交代最新狀況。如果記者會冇新野交待...<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/brain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就係對空氣講野，好似D犬對住條冇人嘅街清場。<br />\n同埋無新野update,記者們仲可以一齊拉隊離場杯葛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />落曬班官嘅面。<br />\n<br />\n等到佢地玩到冇癮唔，唔開每日記招，我地休息夠，再出黎同佢地周旋。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96cf3966ccf10e9008783c395bcd1028817cc46d","tid":1418770,"uid":272573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:21:13.000Z","msg":"自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e995b4dffba97d72a67ff1ddcad276aab998d7e","tid":1418770,"uid":272573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:21:30.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"32ff773262974171d56eddb2bd832860072cc859","tid":1418770,"uid":272573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:21:42.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"9602099d329b3d02476b0b2a986074c3160be894","tid":1418770,"uid":50253,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:22:26.000Z","msg":"收皮啦屌你老母"},{"pid":"4bf8177d33fc5c5ed581435ff7c2c0ad67303de5","tid":1418770,"uid":272573,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"9602099d329b3d02476b0b2a986074c3160be894","tid":1418770,"uid":50253,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:22:26.000Z","msg":"收皮啦屌你老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T20:25:35.000Z","msg":"原因呢？點解唔可行？"},{"pid":"38500be3faf75e3a1d8f98